dungeoncrawler.map

Class Square

  • java.lang.Object
    • dungeoncrawler.map.Square

  • public class Square
extends Object
    This class encapsulates a square. The game map is composed of objects of this class. Each square may contain a game object such as a wall, or a creature such as a monster or the player
